SEARCH

All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Barrel
Represents a Barrel node in the system.
BarrelInt
The remote interface for Barrel objects.
Client
Represents a client that interacts with the gateway to perform search and index operations.
ClientInt
An interface defining methods for updating statistics on the client side.
Database
Database class for handling interactions with the database, including initialization, indexing and searching operations.
Dispatcher
Represents a Dispatcher responsible for managing URL queues and processing.
DispatcherInt
The remote interface for Dispatcher objects.
Downloader
Represents a Downloader node in the system.
Gateway
Represents a Gateway that serves as an interface between clients and the search system.
GatewayBarrel
Represents a GatewayBarrel that serves as an interface between barrels and the gateway.
GatewayBarrelInt
The remote interface for subscribing barrels and checking indexed URLs in a gateway.
GatewayInt
The GatewayInt interface defines remote methods that can be invoked on the Gateway server from a client.
MessageProcessor
Represents a message processor thread in the system.
MessageQueue
Represents a concurrent message queue for storing JSON messages.
Recuperator
Represents a Recuperator thread in the system.
Site
Represents a site that has been indexed by the search engine.
Utils
Utility class to read properties from a file.
